{"tid":100393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲仔「赤口」與女友嗌交　停車場墮樓重創","createTime":"2017-01-30T03:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T08:01:39.000Z","uid":11050,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4daf6916e0f22185065d0c233b3d534a0ce49a","tid":100393,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:51:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170130/bkn-20170130042301566-0130_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170130%2Fbkn-20170130042301566-0130_00822_001.html&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ac23332c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170130/bkn-20170130042301566-0130_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【11:00】姓梁青年經搶救後情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘21歲仔「赤口」與女友爭執後停車場跳樓。今晨4時許，警方接獲一名女子報案，指其男友人於功樂道77號金龍園高處墮下，救護員到場，發現墮樓男子腰部受傷，將傷者送往伊利沙伯醫院急救。警員在場調查後，得悉墮樓男子姓梁(21歲)，與姓秦(21歲)女友較早前因感情問題發生爭執，有人酒醉後走至停車場1樓一躍而下，初步調查案件並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：<br />\n2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：<br />\n2382 0000<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288<br />\n社會福利署：<br />\n2343 2255"},{"pid":"47bc0730837afb23045573812b62105f1dedf846","tid":100393,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"囡囡"},{"pid":"4ea3e8832507814f9845cbae016bef2fe8e8bd40","tid":100393,"uid":10011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:53:31.000Z","msg":"好似係私樓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640086a191877588f29a06917d2132c7ac1e06ca","tid":100393,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"689同張建宗又害人"},{"pid":"50045c65ac435050b1935f1e0cee74dbc9c810d7","tid":100393,"uid":27446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:58:45.000Z","msg":"唔知點解睇左口交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"